</div>
<div>
<p>
<measure quantity="3" unit="years">
<num value="3">三</num>年</measure>
<measure quantity="2" unit="months">
<num value="2">二</num>月</measure>
<num value="39">壬寅</num>
<pc>，</pc>禦前軍器庫火<pc>。</pc>得縱火者<pc>，</pc>
<placeName>楚州</placeName>軍穆椿也<pc>。</pc>全欲銷宋兵備<pc>，</pc>故使椿行<pc>，</pc>且伏奸於外<pc>，</pc>謀入為亂<pc>，</pc>以不得入而止<pc>。</pc>於是先朝兵甲盡喪<pc>。</pc>椿臨刑笑曰<pc>：</pc>
